raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.3.0" %}
{% set name = "jaxlib" %}

package:
  name: jaxlib
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/google/jax/archive/{{ name }}-v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 63897ca8ac9616bc830960912ca0cfacf955c4ae7e3461ff9cd3a2ccc61818f0
  patches:
    - 0001-Don-t-add-dashes-to-version.patch
    - 0001-Patch-pocketfft-for-C-17-osx-64.patch  # [osx and x86_64]
    - 0001-Add-patch-for-google-jax-9534.patch
    - 0001-abseil-wyhash-is-now-called-low_level_hash.patch

build:
  number: 3
  skip: true  # [win or py<37]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - numpy                                  # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - scipy                                  # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - unzip
    - bazel 5.0.0
    - bazel-toolchain
    # need protoc
    - libprotobuf
    # needs protoc-gen-grpc
    - grpc-cpp
    # needs flatc
    - flatbuffers <2.0.6
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - numpy       # [py>=39]
    - numpy 1.19  # [py<39]
    - scipy
    - wheel
    - abseil-cpp
    - flatbuffers <2.0.6
    - grpc-cpp
    - openssl
    - zlib
  run:
    - python
    - absl-py
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - scipy
    - six
    - python-flatbuffers
  run_constrained:   # [osx]
    - __osx >={{ MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET|default("10.9") }}  # [osx]

test:
  files:
    - test_jaxlib.py
  requires:
    - pip
  commands:
    - pip check
    - python test_jaxlib.py
  imports:
    - jaxlib
    # Only this import actually triggers the load of XLA
    - jaxlib.xla_client

about:
  home: http://github.com/google/jax
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Composable transformations of Python+NumPy programs: differentiate, vectorize, JIT to GPU/TPU, and more'
  dev_url: http://github.com/google/jax

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ericmjl
    - xhochy
